Author: Vijay Ramakrishnan

This project is a text-based java blackjack implementation. It assumes a single player-dealer relationship and has functionality of two blackjack actions, "HIT" and "STAND". It also assumes the american version ofthe game, which invovles having a hole card for the dealer. The game restricts atleast 1 chip per hand and the dealer is forced to hit till his deck value is >= 17.

In order to run the application, open the project in your favorite IDE, open the file "GameLoop.java" and run the application. The directions will be indicated on the console as text-based prompts.
